ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER (specific to this skill):

This skill provides AI-assisted suggestions for Chinese personal name generation
based on traditional bazi (eight-character) analysis, dialect phonology checks,
and cultural conventions. It is provided AS-IS for reference and inspiration
only. The bazi calculations performed by language models are not authoritative;
users are strongly advised to consult a qualified命理师 (fortune-teller) before
finalizing any name based on bazi reasoning. Dialect homophone scans rely on the
language model's general knowledge and may miss region-specific pitfalls; users
should verify candidate names with native speakers of relevant dialects before
finalizing. The authors and contributors accept no liability for naming
decisions made on the basis of this skill's output.
